nl.fontys.sebivenlo.statewalker

Interface Device<C extends ContextBase<C,D,S>,D extends Device<C,D,S>,S extends StateBase<C,D,S>>

  • Type Parameters:
    C - Context for this state machine. This
    D - Device for all operations
    S - State to maintain.

    public interface Device<C extends ContextBase<C,D,S>,D extends Device<C,D,S>,S extends StateBase<C,D,S>>
    This empty interface should be extended or implemented to provide the type that is used by the context and or state to operate the device. The 'device' should be understood as any (sub)system that is operated under the control of the state machine implemented by the use of this library.
    Author:
    Pieter van den Hombergh <p.vandenhombergh@fontys.nl>
